text.section:
The records required by this section shall include:
The name and address of the individual who supervised the asbestos removal;
The location of and a description of the project and the amount of asbestos material that was removed;
The starting and completion dates of each instance of removal;
A summary of the procedures that were used to comply with all applicable standards;
The name and address of each asbestos disposal site where the waste containing asbestos was deposited; and
Any other information that the Department requires.
